beer.beer_description:
For our 20th Birthday we brewed our first Double Steam Ale.

We called it Back to the Brewer.

More than a few of us Goats have claimed this hazy, hoppy tribute to two decades of brewing as one of our all-time favourites, so as we celebrate yet another milestone birthday, we’re bringing it back as a birthday gift to ourselves.

This twist on Double Steam Ale takes everything you loved about the original and pushes it into the next level, thanks to the addition of Strata and Sabro hops.

The passionfruit characters of the Galaxy hops are enhanced with brighter tropical notes from the Sabro, while our good mate Strata delivers undertones of dank complexity.

Beer dork & Bartender at Redwood Tasting Room.

Keeping my friends close,
 but my beers closer.

Every loaf of bread is a tragic story of grains 
that could’ve become beer…but didn’t. 

Слава Україні!
Beer, whiskey and coffee are my loves! I use the uni scoring system for my ratings, and love both strong and light beers
